<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="a17Jan1939"><font color="red">17 January 1939</font> <i>NLFF</i> (from Richard de la Mere to Paul L&eacute;on): Our printers &hellip; found those additional corrections for the last galleys, which you have sent me from time to time, most troublesome. To tell you the truth, I think they are reaching the end of their tether &mdash; they have had an appalling job getting through all these revised proofs at such high speed, and they have only done so by working constant overtime at night  </div>
